    #Loading the Dataset
    🧠 Understand this (VERY IMPORTANT)
    🔹 transforms.Resize((224, 224))
        ViT needs fixed image size
        So we resize all images
    🔹 transforms.ToTensor()
        Converts image → numbers (matrix)
        AI models understand numbers, not images
    🔹 datasets.CIFAR10(...)
        Loads dataset of:
        10 classes (cat, dog, car, etc.)
        50,000 training images
    🔹 download=True
        Automatically downloads dataset

        Running this train.py
            --> &"C:\Program Files\Python310\python.exe" train.py
    #Load Vision Transformer (CORE AI PART)
        🧠 Understand this (VERY IMPORTANT)
            🔹 ViTForImageClassification
                Ready-made Vision Transformer
                Already trained on huge dataset
            🔹 from_pretrained(...)
                Downloads model from internet
                You are NOT training from scratch
            🔹 num_labels=10
                CIFAR-10 has 10 classes
                So we change output layer
            Running train.py
                --> & "C:\Program Files\Python310\python.exe" train.py
    #Training Loop (Model Learns Now)

        🧠 Understand this (VERY IMPORTANT)
        🔹 DataLoader
            Feeds data in batches (32 images at a time)
        🔹 device
            Uses GPU if available (faster)
            Else CPU
        🔹 optimizer
            Updates model weights
            Adam = popular optimizer
        🔹 Training Loop

            Each iteration:

            Forward pass → prediction
            Compute loss → error
            Backward pass → gradients
            Update weights

            👉 This is how model learns
        Running train.py
                --> & "C:\Program Files\Python310\python.exe" train.py
				
				
Testing Model (Real Prediction) 🧠 What this does 🔹 train_data[0] Takes one image from dataset 🔹 unsqueeze(0) Converts image → batch format Model expects batch input 🔹 model.eval() Switches model to test mode 🔹 argmax Picks highest probability class